"<command>--disk</command> option, <emphasis>cache=none</emphasis> is "
"recommended if you do not want to use the <command>--unsafe</command> option "
"while doing the migration."
msgstr ""
"あとは <command>virt-install</command> コマンドで &productname; の &vmguest; "
